{
  "texts": [
    "A supervised learning algorithm called Synaptic Weight Association Training (SWAT), a variant of STDP, is used here.",
    "It provides a classification accuracy of 95.3%, 96.7%, and 95.25% for Iris, Wisconsin Breast Cancer, and TI46 speech corpus data-sets, respectively.",
    "The membrane potential dynamics of the model used here are governed by Eq.",
    "An SNN-based computing paradigm has been proposed to provide immunity from device variations for memristive nanodevices in ref.",
    "The neuron model used in this paper is LIF in nature."
  ]
}